    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "This course, microbiology, is itself a very knowledgeable subject and also has bright prospects for future jobs and career perspectives.",
        "Internships are generally not provided by the college, but we are allowed to get internships with our own capabilities.",
        "Most of the companies come to visit here in search of a handsome boy or girl who can represent himself or herself very well.",
        "We also had a good campus recruiting system through which many of us secured good job placements in top companies. However, I believe that the campus recruiting system should be more updated and provide even more opportunities to the students.",
        "We have a games room, a huge library with a wonderful collection of books, and well-updated labs with chemicals and instruments necessary for us.",
        "The college has a canteen, and the food is good and not very expensive. It is comfortable for the students from outside.",
        "If these problems can be resolved one day, the college will become the best college in the region."
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        "This is not a technical or diplomatic college; it is a government college for graduation courses.",
        "The college also offers scholarships for poor students. The college reduces admission fees for poor students and also provides concessions on railway tickets for them.",
        "The bad thing in our college is the presence of bad boys who smoke and bring down the reputation of our college."
      ]
    },
